v1.0:
	Copied libesort from lurker
	Added rollback method for completeness
	Added FORWARD/BACKWARD to match conventional C++
	Renamed seek() with prefix to seekp() for cross-language consistency
	Standardized FORWARD=1, BACKWARD=2
	Default to FORWARD when seeking
	Flushed out all the paramater names so cross-language help works
	Scrapped the concept of versioned databases
	Added C bindings -- header + library
	Added Perl bindings
	Added Python bindings
